@startuml
title SafeCrowd Simple 3-Layer Architecture

skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false

package "application" {
  [safecrowd_app\n(Qt App)] as App
}

package "domain" {
  [safecrowd_domain\n(Scenario / Simulation / Risk)] as Domain
}

package "engine" {
  [ecs_engine\n(ECS / Runtime / Renderer)] as Engine
}

App --> Domain
Domain --> Engine
App --> Engine : viewport only\n(optional)

note right of Engine
  Reusable engine only
  No SafeCrowd logic
  No Qt dependency
end note

note right of Domain
  SafeCrowd rules only
  No Qt dependency
end note

note right of App
  Qt UI and app entry point
end note

@enduml
